narrative:
No non-compliant items identified during this inspection.
The applicant wishes to be licensed by USDA with a new Class C - Exhibitor license.  The applicant will submit all
license applicable fees to the USDA-APHIS-AC Regional Office in Fort Collins, Colorado for processing.  The
mailing address where the applicant needs to submit the license fees is as follows:
     United States Department of Agriculture
     Animal and Plant Health Inspection Service
     Animal Care
     Marketing & Regulatory Program Business Services
     2150 Centre Avenue
     Building B, 3W11
     Fort Collins, CO 80526-8117
No USDA regulated activities are permitted at any location until the USDA license is issued and received by the
applicant.
This inspection and exit interview were conducted with a facility representative.
